import { View, Text, StyleSheet, ScrollView, TouchableOpacity, Linking } from "react-native"
import { SafeAreaView } from "react-native-safe-area-context"

import { theme } from "../theme"

export default function AboutScreen() {
  return (
    <SafeAreaView style={styles.container} edges={["bottom"]}>
      <ScrollView contentContainerStyle={styles.scrollContent}>
        <Text style={styles.title}>About The Project</Text>

        <Text style={styles.description}>
          This project combines computer vision and machine learning to help consumers and farmers identify sweet
          pineapples without cutting them open. Our technology aims to reduce food waste and improve consumer
          satisfaction.
        </Text>

        <View style={styles.section}>
          <Text style={styles.sectionTitle}>Our Mission</Text>
          <Text style={styles.sectionText}>
            Pineapples are one of the most popular tropical fruits worldwide, but selecting a sweet one can be
            challenging. Our mission is to use technology to solve this everyday problem and help reduce food waste
            caused by disappointing fruit purchases.
          </Text>
        </View>

        <View style={styles.section}>
          <Text style={styles.sectionTitle}>The Technology</Text>
          <Text style={styles.sectionText}>
            We've trained our machine learning models on thousands of pineapple samples with verified sweetness levels.
            Our algorithms can identify subtle visual patterns that correlate with sugar content and ripeness.
          </Text>
        </View>

        <View style={styles.section}>
          <Text style={styles.sectionTitle}>Future Plans</Text>
          <Text style={styles.sectionText}>
            We're continuously improving our models and expanding to other fruits and vegetables. Our goal is to create
            a comprehensive suite of tools that help consumers make better food choices.
          </Text>
        </View>

        <View style={styles.buttons}>
          <TouchableOpacity
            style={styles.primaryButton}
            onPress={() => Linking.openURL("mailto:contact@pineappleai.example.com")}
          >
            <Text style={styles.primaryButtonText}>Contact Us</Text>
          </TouchableOpacity>

          <TouchableOpacity
            style={styles.secondaryButton}
            onPress={() => Linking.openURL("https://example.com/research-paper")}
          >
            <Text style={styles.secondaryButtonText}>View Research Paper</Text>
          </TouchableOpacity>
        </View>

        <View style={styles.footer}>
          <Text style={styles.footerText}>Â© 2025 Pineapple Sweetness Predictor</Text>
          <Text style={styles.footerText}>All rights reserved</Text>
        </View>
      </ScrollView>
    </SafeAreaView>
  )
}

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  container: {
    flex: 1,
    backgroundColor: theme.colors.background,
  },
  scrollContent: {
    padding: 20,
  },
  title: {
    fontSize: 24,
    fontWeight: "bold",
    color: theme.colors.text,
    marginBottom: 12,
    textAlign: "center",
  },
  description: {
    fontSize: 16,
    color: theme.colors.textMuted,
    marginBottom: 24,
    textAlign: "center",
  },
  section: {
    marginBottom: 20,
  },
  sectionTitle: {
    fontSize: 18,
    fontWeight: "600",
    color: theme.colors.text,
    marginBottom: 8,
  },
  sectionText: {
    fontSize: 15,
    color: theme.colors.textMuted,
    lineHeight: 22,
  },
  buttons: {
    marginTop: 12,
    marginBottom: 24,
  },
  primaryButton: {
    backgroundColor: theme.colors.yellow[500],
    borderRadius: 8,
    padding: 16,
    alignItems: "center",
    marginBottom: 12,
    ...theme.shadows.sm,
  },
  primaryButtonText: {
    color: "white",
    fontWeight: "600",
    fontSize: 16,
  },
  secondaryButton: {
    backgroundColor: "transparent",
    borderWidth: 1,
    borderColor: theme.colors.border,
    borderRadius: 8,
    padding: 16,
    alignItems: "center",
  },
  secondaryButtonText: {
    color: theme.colors.text,
    fontWeight: "600",
    fontSize: 16,
  },
  footer: {
    marginTop: 24,
    alignItems: "center",
  },
  footerText: {
    fontSize: 14,
    color: theme.colors.textMuted,
    marginBottom: 4,
  },
})
